adblocking_descr.message: Ads can be very annoying. Get rid of ALL online ads!

clear_cache_descr.message: If you visit a website, Chrome stores it in the cache in case you come back later. Clear your cache to remove traces of that website.

clear_cookies_descr.message: Cookies are used to record your visits to a website. Delete cookies stored in your browser so companies cannot recall your previous activity.

clear_downloads_descr.message: After finishing a browsing session, your download history remains on your computer. Clear this list now.

clear_history_descr.message: Remove the list of all your previously accessed websites.

clear_plugindata_descr.message: PlugIns that you have installed might save data on your harddrive without you knowing this. Clear this data now.

clear_storage_descr.message: Clear other data that has been stored on your computer.

enable_https_descr.message: Enable HTTPS for every website to browse more securely.

extDescr.message: Control your online privacy and secure your browsing experience.

manage_facebook_descr.message: Manage your Facebook account settings and change Facebook's

manage_google_descr.message: Manage your Google account settings and change Google's

manage_tracking_descr.message: Change Chrome's privacy settings and tell advertisers that you do not want to be tracked
